      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison metrics (RMSE, bias, coverage probability) computed for NIH and pressure-head QoIs. Prediction intervals from Monte Carlo UQ overlap experimental measurements at all 5 operating points. Coverage probability 92% against 90% target. Confidence rated LOW-MODERATE due to small experimental sample (n=8 per operating point); explicitly documented. Decision team accepted coverage criterion as met."
    },
    {
