      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitored via residual norms and QoI stabilization. All simulations converged to normalized residuals below 1e-5 for continuity and momentum; NIH monitor stabilized to <0.1% change over final 500 iterations. Round-off error assessed as negligible at double precision. Confidence rated MODERATE. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
