      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by independent analyst following documented simulation plan. Boundary conditions, turbulence model selection (SST k-omega), and rotating reference frame configuration verified against checklist. Two independent runs produced NIH within 0.4%. Confidence rated MODERATE. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
