      "rationale": "Reynolds-Averaged Navier-Stokes with SST k-omega turbulence closure selected based on published benchmark performance for rotating blood pump flows. Hemolysis predicted via Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law damage accumulation model. Model form uncertainty explicitly quantified: alternative Taskin model applied in sensitivity study yields NIH within factor of 1.8. Confidence rated LOW due to known power-law model limitations at low-shear conditions; documented honestly. All model form variants remain below clinical threshold."
    },
